Assignments for computer keyboard keys

(Seriously, you need a whole article for this? Fine. Let's get through it.)

For [Wikipedia keyboard shortcuts](/Wikipedia:Keyboard_shortcuts), one might assume there's a simpler way to navigate. There isn't.

